{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the delightful world of fish farming and fishing in this short experimental idler, <strong>Bit-cremental: Fishistry!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287300/extras/Fishing.gif?t=1737766263\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grow and feed your stock, earn money as fisher people reel in mature fish, and upgrade to unlock rare species and colorful new designs, all set in a charming Game Boy-inspired style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287300/extras/PalletSwap.gif?t=1737766263\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fish Growth:</strong> Grow your fish and aquatic creatures from tiny eggs to fully grown wonders.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fish Discovery System:</strong>\u00a0Encounter 24\u00a0different fish types based on rarity, and strive to discover them all!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Idle and Active Gameplay:</strong> Play actively or let your fishery grow while you\u2019re away with automatic idle progression.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Boy Inspired Graphics and Sounds:</strong>\u00a0Play a piece of nostalgia with a retro inspired pixel art from the 90's handheld era with a crunchy audio track.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customize:</strong> Add a personal touch to your fishery with unlockable backgrounds and color palettes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Upgradeable Fishery:</strong> Improve your fishery with upgrades like better feed, fish value, and fish capacity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Simple &amp; Relaxing Play:</strong> A short, laid-back\u00a0gameplay experience perfect for casual gaming with incremental progression.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Catch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/a18e07772443d1fd1fe734e5045f7e3ea2edfc79.jpg"},{"name":"Gashapon Enthusiast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/6b30750e9e94bcc706c284f1d875a2bf5ed13299.jpg"},{"name":"Collector Extraordinaire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/ab353708e206f32464acfd517fc9147115217b41.jpg"},{"name":"Making Waves","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/0fa1900d877f906f212dcc0ff63503ed7f00fd05.jpg"},{"name":"Fishing Empire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/887ffd25c4c4b7e6a1dd64998d413cee7e007cb3.jpg"},{"name":"Specialist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/75ee981710dcca9da2924d6858ef9254514098f6.jpg"},{"name":"Jack of All Trades","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/23e574850531d615e23da8c9b822cf5c2bb16a36.jpg"},{"name":"Aesthetic Aficionado","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/8f1f8cbff56bf59972c89da03a414777d64575ba.jpg"},{"name":"Legendary Treasure","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/5353b8364c1e98be387218de82b8cf89e68b266d.jpg"},{"name":"Fish Whisperer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3287300/c62f236c3a253f49ef54f956b667b32e56ea3376.jpg"}],"total":10},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737766263","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287300/page.bg.jpg?t=1737766263","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287300/840